high_descs: turn around and move forward to the sink that is to the right of the bath tub, turn right to face the white cabinet
pick up the pink bar of soap that is on the cabinet
turn to the left to face the sink
put the bar of soap in to the sink, rinse it off and remove the soap from the sink
turn around and then turn to the right to move forward to the trash can that is under the window and to the right of the toilet
put the bar of soap in to the trash can
anns.task_desc: put a rinsed bar of soap in to the trash can

high_descs: turn to face radiator cover next to sink
pick up soap bar from radiator cover
wash soap in sink, pick up soap from sink
walk to face garbage bin next to toilet
anns.task_desc: put wash soap bar in garbage bin

high_descs: Turn around and move toward the sink, turn right to face the shelf on the wall.
Pick up the bar of soap from the left side of the shelf.
Carry the soap and turn to the sink on the right.
Place the soap inside the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the soap.
Hold the soap and turn around. Turn right and move back to the trash can.
Place the soap inside the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a bar of soap and throw it away.
